HEADWORD: coffeeberry
<hw>coffeeberry</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>an evergreen shrub of Western
U.S. (<spn>Rhamnus californicus</spn>), bearing small red or black
fruits; -- called also the <altname>California
buckthorn</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> California buckthorn, California coffee,
<spn>Rhamnus californicus</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
